        <div><div class="fragment" data-path="/cc-shared/fragments/products/photoshop-lightroom/faq"><div class="section static-links xxl-spacing-bottom" data-has-placeholders="true">
  <div class="text max-width-8-desktop center xxxl-spacing-top s-spacing-bottom left-mobile text-block con-block" data-block-status="loaded" data-block="">
    <div class="foreground">
      <div class="body-m">
        <h2 id="questions-we-have-answers" class="heading-xl">Questions? We have answers.</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion-container seo static-links con-block max-width-10-desktop" data-block-status="loaded" data-block=""><div class="descr-list accordion foreground" id="accordion-1" role="presentation"><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-1" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-1" daa-ll="open-1--What is Lightroom">
      What is Lightroom?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-1" id="accordion-1-content-1" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Lightroom is the cloud-based service that gives you everything you need to create, edit, organize, store, and share your photos across any device.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-2" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-2" daa-ll="open-2--Can I buy Lightroom as a standalone app">
      Can I buy Lightroom as a standalone app?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-2" id="accordion-1-content-2" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes, you can buy Lightroom as a single app. Purchase Lightroom <a href="/creativecloud/plans/?filter=photography">now</a>.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-3" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-3" daa-ll="open-3--How much does Lightroom cost">
      How much does Lightroom cost?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-3" id="accordion-1-content-3" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>You can purchase Lightroom with an annual plan starting at <span is="inline-price" data-display-per-unit="false" data-display-recurrence="true" data-display-tax="false" data-force-tax-exclusive="false" data-quantity="1" data-template="price" data-wcs-osi="YbmrrnDXjKp75tHcS_wDjwLhuZl3uldCu00qBXGJFMc" class="placeholder-resolved"><span class="price"><span class="price-currency-symbol">US$</span><span class="price-currency-space disabled"></span><span class="price-integer">11</span><span class="price-decimals-delimiter">.</span><span class="price-decimals">99</span><span class="price-recurrence">/mo</span><span class="price-unit-type disabled"></span><span class="price-tax-inclusivity disabled"></span></span></span>  for the annual billed monthly plan or <span is="inline-price" data-display-per-unit="false" data-display-recurrence="true" data-display-tax="false" data-force-tax-exclusive="false" data-quantity="1" data-template="price" data-wcs-osi="90bsAnJa1V6a6nIc9MWpQLwGHbPwAhcqOp268hEKDi4" class="placeholder-resolved"><span class="price"><span class="price-currency-symbol">US$</span><span class="price-currency-space disabled"></span><span class="price-integer">119</span><span class="price-decimals-delimiter">.</span><span class="price-decimals">88</span><span class="price-recurrence">/yr</span><span class="price-unit-type disabled"></span><span class="price-tax-inclusivity disabled"></span></span></span>.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-4" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-4" daa-ll="open-4--How much cloud storage comes with Lightroom">
      How much cloud storage comes with Lightroom?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-4" id="accordion-1-content-4" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>The Lightroom plan comes with 1TB. You can always add more storage to your plan from your Adobe account. <a href="https://helpx.adobe.com/x-productkb/global/upgrade-creative-cloud-storage.html">Learn how to upgrade your storage plan.</a></div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-5" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-5" daa-ll="open-5--Can I install Lightroom on multiple devices">
      Can I install Lightroom on multiple devices?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-5" id="accordion-1-content-5" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes, your individual license lets you install Lightroom on more than one computer. You can activate it on two but only use it on one computer at a time.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-6" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-6" daa-ll="open-6--How do I use Lightroom">
      How do I use Lightroom?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-6" id="accordion-1-content-6" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Learn the basics or refine your skills with Lightroom tutorials designed to inspire. <a href="https://helpx.adobe.com/lightroom-cc/tutorials.html">Explore all Lightroom tutorials.</a></div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-7" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-7" daa-ll="open-7--How do I update Lightroom">
      How do I update Lightroom?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-7" id="accordion-1-content-7" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>You can update Lightroom within your Adobe account. <a href="https://helpx.adobe.com/creative-cloud/help/creative-cloud-updates.html">Learn how to update Lightroom</a>.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-8" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-8" daa-ll="open-8--Is Lightroom free on iPhone">
      Is Lightroom free on iPhone?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-8" id="accordion-1-content-8" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes, Lightroom for mobile is a free app for iOS and Android that gives you a powerful yet simple solution for capturing, editing, and sharing photos. You can also upgrade to premium features and work across any device. <a href="https://helpx.adobe.com/mobile-apps/help/lightroom-mobile-faq.html">Learn how to upgrade to premium features</a>.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-9" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-9" daa-ll="open-9--What s the difference between Lightroom and Lightroom Classic">
      What’s the difference between Lightroom and Lightroom Classic?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-9" id="accordion-1-content-9" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Both Lightroom and Lightroom Classic offer most of the same features, but Lightroom lets you edit and organize your photos across desktop, mobile, and web, while Lightroom Classic is optimized for desktop use. Lightroom Classic is included in the Lightroom plan. <a href="/products/photoshop-lightroom-classic/lightroom-cc-vs-lightroom-classic/">Find out more about the difference between Lightroom and Lightroom Classic</a>.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-10" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-10" daa-ll="open-10--What s the difference between Lightroom and Photoshop">
      What’s the difference between Lightroom and Photoshop?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-10" id="accordion-1-content-10" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Lightroom and Photoshop are powerful image editing tools. Use Lightroom to easily edit your photos to make them match your vision. For more transformational edits like compositing or fine retouching, try Photoshop. <a href="/creativecloud/photography/lightroom-vs-photoshop/" data-has-dnt="true">Learn more about the difference between Lightroom and Photoshop</a>.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-11" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-11" daa-ll="open-11--What is Lightroom CC">
      What is Lightroom CC?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-11" id="accordion-1-content-11" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>When Lightroom first launched it was called Lightroom CC. We have since renamed it to just Lightroom.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-12" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-12" daa-ll="open-12--Is there a student discount for Lightroom">
      Is there a student discount for Lightroom?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-12" id="accordion-1-content-12" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes, students and teachers can get Lightroom as part of the Creative Cloud Pro plan for a reduced price of <span is="inline-price" data-display-per-unit="false" data-display-recurrence="true" data-display-tax="false" data-force-tax-exclusive="false" data-quantity="1" data-template="price" data-wcs-osi="Hnk2P6L5wYhnpZLFYTW5upuk2Y3AJXlso8VGWQ0l2TI" class="placeholder-resolved"><span class="price"><span class="price-currency-symbol">US$</span><span class="price-currency-space disabled"></span><span class="price-integer">19</span><span class="price-decimals-delimiter">.</span><span class="price-decimals">99</span><span class="price-recurrence">/mo</span><span class="price-unit-type disabled"></span><span class="price-tax-inclusivity disabled"></span></span></span> for the first year. The plan features 20+ desktop and mobile apps including Lightroom, Photoshop, Acrobat Pro, Illustrator, InDesign, XD, Premiere, and more. At the end of the first year, the subscription will be automatically billed at the standard rate, currently <span is="inline-price" data-display-per-unit="false" data-display-recurrence="true" data-display-tax="false" data-force-tax-exclusive="false" data-quantity="1" data-template="price" data-wcs-osi="DFaWY47EmtzYVOApli4DjncThGsfaeCSDZRoHkC8pGY" class="placeholder-resolved"><span class="price"><span class="price-currency-symbol">US$</span><span class="price-currency-space disabled"></span><span class="price-integer">39</span><span class="price-decimals-delimiter">.</span><span class="price-decimals">99</span><span class="price-recurrence">/mo</span><span class="price-unit-type disabled"></span><span class="price-tax-inclusivity disabled"></span></span></span>, unless you elect to change or cancel your subscription. <a href="/creativecloud/buy/students/">Learn more about the Creative Cloud Pro plan for students and teachers</a>.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-13" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-13" daa-ll="open-13--How do I cancel a Lightroom subscription">
      How do I cancel a Lightroom subscription?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-13" id="accordion-1-content-13" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>To cancel your Lightroom subscription, navigate to your <a href="https://account.adobe.com/plans">Adobe account page</a>. Locate your plan name and click Manage Plans. Then click Cancel Plan. Indicate your cancellation reason, and then click continue. Follow the onscreen instructions to finish your cancellation. <a href="https://helpx.adobe.com/manage-account/using/cancel-subscription.html">Get step-by-step cancellation instructions</a>.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-14" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-14" daa-ll="open-14--Are the new Lightroom features also available on the web">
      Are the new Lightroom features also available on the web?
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-14" id="accordion-1-content-14" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes. You can now access the power of AI on Lightroom for the web (<a href="https://lightroom.adobe.com/">Lightroom.adobe.com</a>), starting with our selective adjustment tools. AI masking for Select Subject, Sky, and Background are available on web, plus new Adaptive Presets including Whiten Teeth, Glamour, and more.</div></div></div></div>
